```python
def insert_after_character(string):
    return string.replace('U', 'UU')

print(insert_after_character('Hello World'))
print(insert_after_character('This is a test'))
print(insert_after_character('Umbrella'))
print(insert_after_character('U'))
print(insert_after_character('UUUUU'))
```

```
Hello World
This is a test
```
